mm2 Asia suddenly come alive . 48-52 so fast. should be news coming?Lets go Vividthree $0.042/$0.043 buy call.

Vividthree is vested in SkyArk Chronicles through GammAr. They seem to be doing a good job publicising and marketing this game now as they embark on the final stages based on the info on website that they will launch in 3rd Quarter 2022.A successful game launch would be a major game changer and catalyst for a big big run.I look forward to hearing more updates from their IR side as they start to prepare for the game launch.If this game does take off and gain popularity and garner user and fan base  no reason this cannot turn into a MULTIBAGGER. Fingers crossed.Just for reference  the Sky Ark Chronicles telegram channel has 18.5k users.PS: Could mm2 asia sudden rally today be due to this? I guess only time can tell.

I think Vividthree will be a worthy punt at current prices. $0.042/$0.043 looks too bottomish here  considering that insiders did deal at $0.08x /. The last placement for VV3 was at $0.058x too.They announced recently that Crypto/Metaverseguy Jonathan Zhang has taken up executive role and he will be in charge of fund raising in coming months. Hence  hoping this is a placement deal at a price closer to last placement. Last round placement deal  they gapped up at least 15 pips from what i could recall.
